title: Kalooki's
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Beer/Wine, Caribbean, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Open-air, beachside restaurant with full bar and live music sometimes. Has a vegetarian section on the menu called "Veggie-My-Table," which offers a black bean burger that comes with with mango chutney sauce, sweet potato fries, and a salad. There's also a curried tofu dish that's served with jasmine rice and mango chutney sauce.
